 be a\npromising tool to constrain (R0, Vsun), given that Gaia is expected to discover\nmany nearby HVSs in the near future.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 23 Apr 2018 17:34:09 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 29 Oct 2018 18:45:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-12-19"}
