oresistance in high field is probably due to\nfield-dependent mobilities, another feature of semimetals under high magnetic\nfields.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Apr 2018 00:58:30 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Sep 2018 08:40:08 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-09-17"}
