gment STM images and other data. To demonstrate the potential of\nour approach, we apply it to actual STM images of cyanide monolayers on\nAu\\{111\\} and present their corresponding segmentation results.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Apr 2018 08:16:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-25"}
