e given\nand the use of modern magnetic modelling tools is discussed, with a few\nillustrative examples. An approach is chosen where the accent is less on\ncompleteness and rigorousness (because this has already been done) and more on\nexplaining and illustrating the main principles that are used in medical\ncyclotrons. Sometimes a more industrial viewpoint is taken. The use of\ncomplicated formulae is limited.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 24 Apr 2018 11:32:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-04-25"}
